---
import gameplay1 from '../assets/images/gameplay1.png';
---

<section id="features" class="features section">
  <div class="features-bg"></div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-badge">Game Features</div>
      <h2>Epic Cheese Battles Await</h2>
      <p>Discover what makes Cheese Chompers 3D the most entertaining rodent rumble on the web! Developed using Unity WebGL technology, this physics-based knockout game delivers non-stop action.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm0 18c-4.41 0-8-3.59-8-8s3.59-8 8-8 8 3.59 8 8-3.59 8-8 8zm-5-9h10v2H7z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-content">
          <h3>Wobbly 3D Rats</h3>
          <p>Control comical rodent characters with unpredictable physics that create hilarious moments with every movement.</p>
          <div class="feature-tag">Physics-Based</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M12 16c1.66 0 3-1.34 3-3 0-1.66-1.34-3-3-3s-3 1.34-3 3c0 1.66 1.34 3 3 3zm-7 0c1.66 0 3-1.34 3-3 0-1.66-1.34-3-3-3s-3 1.34-3 3c0 1.66 1.34 3 3 3zm14 0c1.66 0 3-1.34 3-3 0-1.66-1.34-3-3-3s-3 1.34-3 3c0 1.66 1.34 3 3 3z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-content">
          <h3>Explosive Knockouts</h3>
          <p>Enjoy spectacular visual effects when you successfully push opponents off the arena, adding satisfaction to every victory.</p>
          <div class="feature-tag">Visual Effects</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M13.49 5.48c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2s-.9-2-2-2-2 .9-2 2 .9 2 2 2zm-3.6 13.9l1-4.4 2.1 2v6h2v-7.5l-2.1-2 .6-3c1.3 1.5 3.3 2.5 5.5 2.5v-2c-1.9 0-3.5-1-4.3-2.4l-1-1.6c-.4-.6-1-1-1.7-1-.3 0-.5.1-.8.1l-5.2 2.2v4.7h2v-3.4l1.8-.7-1.6 8.1-4.9-1-.4 2 7 1.4z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-content">
          <h3>Speed-Boosting Flips</h3>
          <p>Perform mid-air flips to gain temporary speed advantages, perfect for chasing opponents or escaping dangerous situations.</p>
          <div class="feature-tag">Special Moves</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M21 6H3c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v8c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h18c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V8c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 10H3V8h18v8zM6 15h2v-2h2v-2H8V9H6v2H4v2h2z"/>
            <path d="M14.5 13.5a1.5 1.5 0 100-3 1.5 1.5 0 000 3z"/>
            <path d="M18.5 10.5a1.5 1.5 0 100 3 1.5 1.5 0 000-3z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-content">
          <h3>Dynamic Collisions</h3>
          <p>Experience realistic physics interactions between characters, creating unpredictable and entertaining gameplay moments.</p>
          <div class="feature-tag">Realistic Physics</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="500">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M19 3H5c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v14c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h14c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 16H5V5h14v14zM7 10h2v7H7zm4-3h2v10h-2zm4 6h2v4h-2z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-content">
          <h3>Instant Browser Play</h3>
          <p>Jump into the cheesy chaos directly from your web browser without any downloads or installations required.</p>
          <div class="feature-tag">No Download</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="600">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M11 9H9V2H7v7H5V2H3v7c0 2.12 1.66 3.84 3.75 3.97V22h2.5v-9.03C11.34 12.84 13 11.12 13 9V2h-2v7zm5-3v8h2.5v8H21V2c-2.76 0-5 2.24-5 4z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-content">
          <h3>Cheese-Themed Arena</h3>
          <p>Battle in a vibrant, cheese-inspired environment that adds a unique and whimsical backdrop to the rodent rumble.</p>
          <div class="feature-tag">Unique Setting</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="700">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M21 2H3c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v12c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h7v2H8v2h8v-2h-2v-2h7c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V4c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 14H3V4h18v12z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-content">
          <h3>Cross-Platform Compatibility</h3>
          <p>Play on desktop browsers with optimal performance. While primarily designed for computers, the simple controls make it accessible across different devices.</p>
          <div class="feature-tag">Accessibility</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="features-showcase">
      <div class="features-image">
        <div class="image-glow"></div>
        <img src={gameplay1.src} alt="Cheese Chompers 3D Gameplay" width="800" height="450" loading="lazy" class="main-image" />
      </div>
      <div class="features-cta">
        <h3>Ready to Rumble?</h3>
        <p>Join thousands of players in the ultimate cheese battle!</p>
        <a href="#game" class="btn">Play Now</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .features {
    background-color: var(--color-background);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .features-bg {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, rgba(255, 87, 34, 0.05) 0%, transparent 30%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 80% 70%, rgba(140, 82, 255, 0.05) 0%, transparent 30%);
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto 4rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .section-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary), var(--color-tertiary));
    color: var(--color-white);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    color: var(--color-white);
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--color-primary), var(--color-secondary));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  .section-header p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .feature-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(42, 42, 64, 0.8), rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.8));
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
    padding: 2rem;
    box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
    transition: all var(--transition-medium) ease;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .feature-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--color-primary), var(--color-secondary));
    transform: scaleX(0);
    transform-origin: left;
    transition: transform var(--transition-medium) ease;
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-10px);
    box-shadow: var(--box-shadow-hover);
    border-color: rgba(255, 87, 34, 0.2);
  }

  .feature-card:hover::before {
    transform: scaleX(1);
  }

  .feature-icon {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 70px;
    height: 70px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 87, 34, 0.2), rgba(255, 214, 0, 0.1));
    border-radius: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    transition: all var(--transition-medium) ease;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(255, 87, 34, 0.2);
  }

  .feature-card:hover .feature-icon {
    transform: scale(1.1) rotate(5deg);
    box-shadow: var(--neon-glow);
  }

  .feature-content {
    position: relative;
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-white);
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .feature-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .feature-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 214, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .features-showcase {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .features-image {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
    transition: all var(--transition-medium) ease;
  }

  .image-glow {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(255, 87, 34, 0.3) 0%, transparent 70%);
    z-index: 1;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity var(--transition-medium) ease;
  }

  .features-image:hover .image-glow {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .main-image {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
    transition: transform var(--transition-medium) ease;
    transform: scale(1);
    display: block;
  }

  .features-image:hover .main-image {
    transform: scale(1.03);
  }

  .features-cta {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(42, 42, 64, 0.8), rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.8));
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 87, 34, 0.2);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .features-cta h3 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .features-cta p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .features-cta .btn {
    padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    animation: pulse 2s infinite;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1200px) {
    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .section-header h2 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .features-showcase {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .features-cta {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .section-header {
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .section-header h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .section-header p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .features-grid {
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 576px) {
    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .feature-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .section-badge {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      padding: 0.4rem 1.2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
